{"id": 231279370, "title": "Pin Zhi, Bhutan\u2019s first 2D adventure game now available online", "text": "Bhutan\u2019s first 2D adventure game, Pin Zhi is now available online. It was launched on itch.io, a game distribution website on Thursday. As of now, about 20 copies of the game have been ordered by Bhutanese gamers and a few copies were sold from the website. It will also be made available on Steam from the 18th of this month. A group of DeSuups working for an IT company in Thimphu TechPark called Green E-Integrated Private Limited developed the game. Karma Wangdi", "summary": "<p>Bhutan\u2019s first 2D adventure game, Pin Zhi is now available online. It was launched on itch.io, a game distribution website on Thursday. As of now, about 20 copies of the game have been ordered by Bhutanese gamers and a few copies were sold from the website. It will also be made available on Steam from [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.bbs.bt/news/?p=204718\">Pin Zhi, Bhutan\u2019s first 2D adventure game now available online</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.bbs.bt/news\">BBSCL</a>.</p>", "url": "https://www.bbs.bt/news/?p=204718", "image": "http://www.bbs.bt/news/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2D-GAME.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-08 13:45:10", "author": "kip chu", "authors": ["kip chu"], "language": "en", "source_country": "BT", "sentiment": -0.166}